<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <title>Graphic Design</title>
</head>
<body id="mainbackgrounddesign">
    <%- include ('partials/navbar.ejs') %>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-4">
            <h2 id="ds1">Fundamentals Of Design</h2>
            <p id="ds1">Below are some of my works. Click on each to explore more about them!</p>
        </div>

        <!-- GA -->
        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <!-- Clickable Image that triggers the modal -->
                <a href="#" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#project1Modal">
                    <img src="MB.png" class="img-fluid" alt="Project 1">
                </a> 
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                <h3 id="ds2">Design GA</h3>
                <p id="ds2">
                I have 4 pages in total. Homepage, About Us page, Portfolio page and Contact Us page.
                Additionally, I also have a name card, sketches and chat stickers representing my business.
                </p>

                <p>
                My business' name is Harutobi, a swimming company, and my role is a graphic designer/CEO.
                The main purpose of my business is to invite poeple of all ages to swim either competitively or 
                casually, at the same time, also making friends.
                </p>

                <p>
                In order to attract more people, I created a drawing of a jacket using illustrator. On the back of
                the jacket has the swimming company/club, 'Harutobi', plus I also plan to give out free goggles of 
                different colours for all early bird sign up specials. Lastly, the moodbaord shows the color scheme I 
                feel is most suited to swimming and friendship, blue and yellow. It also somewhat represents me too.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Modals Section -->
        <!-- GA Modal with Carousel -->
        <div class="modal fade" id="project1Modal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="project1ModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <!-- Bootstrap Carousel for GA Images -->
                        <div id="project1Carousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                            <div class="carousel-inner">
                                <!-- First Image -->
                                <div class="carousel-item active">
                                    <img src="DesignGA1.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Design GA Image 1">
                                </div>
                                <!-- Second Image -->
                                <div class="carousel-item">
                                    <img src="DesignGA2.PNG" class="d-block w-100" alt="Design GA Image 2">
                                </div>
                                <!-- Third Image -->
                                <div class="carousel-item">
                                    <img src="DesignGA3.PNG" class="d-block w-100" alt="Design GA Image 3">
                                </div>
                                <!-- Fourth Image -->
                                <div class="carousel-item">
                                    <img src="DesignGA4.PNG" class="d-block w-100" alt="Design GA Image 4">
                                </div>
                                <!-- Fifth Image -->
                                <div class="carousel-item">
                                    <img src="DesignGA5.PNG" class="d-block w-100" alt="Design GA Image 5">
                                </div>
                                <!-- Sixth Image -->
                                <div class="carousel-item">
                                    <img src="DesignGA6.PNG" class="d-block w-100" alt="Design GA Image 6">
                                </div>
                                <!-- Seventh Image -->
                                <div class="carousel-item">
                                    <img src="MB.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Design GA Image 7">
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Carousel Controls -->
                            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#project1Carousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                            </button>
                            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#project1Carousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Project 2 -->
        <div class="row mb-5">
           <div class="col-md-6">
              <!-- Clickable Image that triggers the modal -->
              <a href="#" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#project2Modal">
                 <img src="Design2.png" class="img-fluid" alt="Project 2">
              </a>
           </div>
           <div class="col-md-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
               <h3 id="ds2">Design In Class Works</h3>
               <p id="ds2">
                These are some of the works I have done in class over 13 lessons. 
                </p>

                <p>
                Each lesson I have learnt new techniques and have applied and enhanced works to be used
                in my Design GA Project on top. Some of the new techniques I have learnt include the use 
                of illustrator and photoshop. Some include using genetics AI, foreshadowing, layer masking
                etc.
               </p>
           </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Modals Section -->
        <!-- Project 2 Modal with Carousel -->
        <div class="modal fade" id="project2Modal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="project2ModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <!-- Bootstrap Carousel for Project 2 Images -->
                        <div id="project2Carousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                            <div class="carousel-inner">
                                <!-- First Image -->
                                <div class="carousel-item active">
                                    <img src="Design1.PNG" class="d-block w-100" alt="Coding Works Image 1">
